  "prompt": "Where we can buy books online in Pune?",
  "response": "In Pune, you can buy books online from several reputable platforms. Here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Amazon** - Offers a vast selection of books across genres, often with competitive prices and fast delivery options.\n\n2. **Flipkart** - Another major online retailer in India, Flipkart has a large collection of books and offers various discounts and deals.\n\n3. **Bookish Santa** - An online bookstore that specializes in new books, used books, and has a variety of genres.\n\n4. **Snapdeal** - This e-commerce platform also has a good selection of books and often runs special promotions.\n\n5. **Oxford Bookstore** - An established bookstore with an online presence that offers a curated selection of books.\n\n6. **Infibeam** - This online marketplace offers books along with various other products.\n\n7. **BooksMyKids** - Focused on children's literature, this site has a great selection for young readers.\n\n8. **Sapna Book House** - This platform provides a wide range of books and emphasizes regional literature.\n\n9. **Pustak.org** - An online platform where you can buy and sell second-hand books.\n\n10. **Kobo** - For e-books, Kobo offers a selection that can be read on various devices.\n\nThese platforms provide convenient options for purchasing books online in Pune and often feature home delivery services.",
